      <title>美联储会议后股市上涨或为抛售火上浇油</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/stocks-post-fed-rally-risks-adding-accelerant-fuel-to-selloff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管股市在上周美联储期待已久的降息之后出现上涨，但伴随上涨的也是一丝不安感。]]></description>
